{
  "stem": "14897.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We went every winter for two or three weeks to a winter resort-- which I'm going to visit when I will be in Poland in June of this year.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's the sort of thing that we all did there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We would ski and skate during the day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then the children-- and I was-- I was always a big operator as a child.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I would arrange for us to put on a performance towards the end of our stay of different skits, and, and songs, and all kinds of little things.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we would-- we would charge for attending this performance.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Of course, all the parents came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then I remember that on the last day, we would go to a Jewish orphanage to whom we donated the money that we had collected.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And because I was the big organizer and producer of this affair, I always went, you know, to this.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And really, when I think about it, now I kind of cringe that they would take this child, introduce me to this whole class of children.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And probably was rather humiliating for them to have me come up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I brought the money and so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Not, not the best-- not psychologically the most clever situation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But that's-- i think it inculcated in us the importance of sharing what we had with other people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The school that I went to, for example, you had to bring two lunches-- one for you and one for another school, which was like a sister school where the children were poor.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we provided the lunches for them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To my knowledge.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I do-- my father knew, of course, a lot of people who were not Jewish, but we lived in a Jewish part of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
